      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>soy</strong> <strong>tofu </strong>to the pan with the<strong> ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>ground cumin </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to crisp</p>",
